column5: will be fishing wabigoon 8/18-25. have fished area but never wabigoon. current reports,baits etc. would be very much app. thanks, swf
looks like no one goes there, must be either really good, or not so hot.
pwt was there end of july. caught lots of 1.5-2lb fish. almost any bait worked on any rock piles or around weeds.
